body:
we had the same issue with our installation.

oc version 5.0.3  edit: same with 5.0.5 now
php 5.3.3
rhel 6.4

with ldap settings *user login filter* set to 
    
    (&(uid=%uid)(<condition1>)(<condition2>))

and *user list filter* being empty sharing is impossible (except to admin / local users). an excerpt from the logfile is appended.
when setting *user list filter* to something non-empty like

    (&(<condition1>)(<condition2>))

sharing will work. so *user list filter* should be either marked as mandatory or the current behaviour should be fixed.


best regards
roland

